France\", \"score\": 0.9937611859854293, \"rank\": 0.006251960072789897, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Sports Scene Copied Erislandy Alvarez\", \"from\": 205, \"to\": 242}, {\"ngram\": \"the men's 63.5-kilogram division\", \"from\": 276, \"to\": 308}, {\"ngram\": \"gold medal\", \"from\": 316, \"to\": 326}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2024 Summer Olympics\", \"from\": 330, \"to\": 354}]}, {\"sentence\": \"/CFP Cuba's Erislandy Alvarez triumphed in the men's 63.5-kilogram boxing division to give his country its first gold medal in the sport at the 2024 Paris Summer Olympics, after defeating home favorite Sofiane Ouhima of France in a 3-2 split decision on Wednesday.\", \"from\": 391, \"to\": 656, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 397, \"end\": 401, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cuba\", \"score\": 0.9852139465174449, \"rank\": 0.014946915913826499, \"text\": \"Cuba\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cuba\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cuba\"}, {\"begin\": 612, \"end\": 618, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9937611859854293, \"rank\": 0.006251960072789897, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"/CFP\", \"from\": 391, \"to\": 395}, {\"ngram\": \"the men's 63.5-kilogram boxing division\", \"from\": 434, \"to\": 473}, {\"ngram\": \"his country\", \"from\": 482, \"to\": 493}, {\"ngram\": \"its first gold medal\", \"from\": 494, \"to\": 514}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 518, \"to\": 527}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2024 Paris Summer Olympics\", \"from\": 531, \"to\": 561}, {\"ngram\": \"favorite Sofiane Ouhima\", \"from\": 584, \"to\": 607}, {\"ngram\": \"a 3-2 split decision\", \"from\": 621, \"to\": 641}, {\"ngram\": \"Wednesday\", \"from\": 645, \"to\": 654}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Alvarez was in a great form in the first round, fighting at distance and beating Ouhima to the punch on multiple occasions, to take the round on every scorecard.\", \"from\": 658, \"to\": 819, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Alvarez\", \"from\": 658, \"to\": 665}, {\"ngram\": \"a great form\", \"from\": 673, \"to\": 685}, {\"ngram\": \"the first round\", \"from\": 689, \"to\": 704}, {\"ngram\": \"distance\", \"from\": 718, \"to\": 726}, {\"ngram\": \"Ouhima\", \"from\": 739, \"to\": 745}, {\"ngram\": \"the punch\", \"from\": 749, \"to\": 758}, {\"ngram\": \"multiple occasions\", \"from\": 762, \"to\": 780}, {\"ngram\": \"the round\", \"from\": 790, \"to\": 799}, {\"ngram\": \"every scorecard\", \"from\": 803, \"to\": 818}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The second and third rounds were much closer, with the Frenchman chasing down the slicker Cuban.\", \"from\": 820, \"to\": 916, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 910, \"end\": 915, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cuba\", \"score\": 0.6782938232816572, \"rank\": 0.47428075055003843, \"text\": \"Cuban\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cuba\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cuba\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The second and third rounds\", \"from\": 820, \"to\": 847}, {\"ngram\": \"the Frenchman\", \"from\": 871, \"to\": 884}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But much to the disagreement of the home crowd, Alvarez was able to outlast Ouhima through the third, winning three of the five judges' favor.\", \"from\": 917, \"to\": 1059, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the disagreement\", \"from\": 929, \"to\": 945}, {\"ngram\": \"the home crowd\", \"from\": 949, \"to\": 963}, {\"ngram\": \"Alvarez\", \"from\": 965, \"to\": 972}, {\"ngram\": \"Ouhima\", \"from\": 993, \"to\": 999}, {\"ngram\": \"the five judges' favor\", \"from\": 1036, \"to\": 1058}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ukraine's Oleksandr Khyzhniak claimed the bronze in another tight split decision over Nurbek Oralbay of Kazakhstan in the 80-kilogram event to win his country's first boxing medal in Paris.\", \"from\": 1061, \"to\": 1250, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1061, \"end\": 1068, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\", \"score\": 0.9960295620791054, \"rank\": 0.003713954025047842, \"text\": \"Ukraine\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\"}, {\"begin\": 1071, \"end\": 1090, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oleksandr_Khyzhniak\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Oleksandr Khyzhniak\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oleksandr_Khyzhniak\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oleksandr_Khyzhniak\"}, {\"begin\": 1147, \"end\": 1161, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nurbek_Oralbay\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Nurbek Oralbay\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nurbek_Oralbay\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nurbek_Oralbay\"}, {\"begin\": 1165, \"end\": 1175, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kazakhstan\", \"score\": 0.9999810034190822, \"rank\": 1.6648401243279054e-05, \"text\": \"Kazakhstan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kazakhstan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kazakhstan\"}, {\"begin\": 1244, \"end\": 1249, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999922693, \"rank\": 7.678867159290014e-12, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the bronze\", \"from\": 1099, \"to\": 1109}, {\"ngram\": \"another tight split decision\", \"from\": 1113, \"to\": 1141}, {\"ngram\": \"the 80-kilogram event\", \"from\": 1179, \"to\": 1200}, {\"ngram\": \"his country's first boxing medal\", \"from\": 1208, \"to\": 1240}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The opening two rounds were very close, as neither was able to nullify the other's offense while remaining defensively secure.\", \"from\": 1252, \"to\": 1378, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The opening two rounds\", \"from\": 1252, \"to\": 1274}, {\"ngram\": \"neither\", \"from\": 1295, \"to\": 1302}, {\"ngram\": \"the other's offense\", \"from\": 1323, \"to\": 1342}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But in the third round, Khyzhniak showed his class and began to pick Oralbay apart, taking the round on all of the judges' scorecards and securing a bitterly close 3-2 split decision.\", \"from\": 1379, \"to\": 1562, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the third round\", \"from\": 1386, \"to\": 1401}, {\"ngram\": \"Khyzhniak\", \"from\": 1403, \"to\": 1412}, {\"ngram\": \"his class\", \"from\": 1420, \"to\": 1429}, {\"ngram\": \"Oralbay\", \"from\": 1448, \"to\": 1455}, {\"ngram\": \"the round\", \"from\": 1470, \"to\": 1479}, {\"ngram\": \"the judges' scorecards\", \"from\": 1490, \"to\": 1512}, {\"ngram\": \"a bitterly close 3-2 split decision\", \"from\": 1526, \"to\": 1561}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the men's over-92-kilogram division, gold medal favorite Bakhodir Jalolov of Uzbekistan thoroughly outclassed Germany's Nelvie Raman Tiafack to claim a unanimous decision and reach the final.\", \"from\": 1564, \"to\": 1758, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1694, \"end\": 1699, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raman_scattering\", \"score\": 0.8655497502106285, \"rank\": 0.136598260854552, \"text\": \"Raman\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raman_scattering\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raman_scattering\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the men's over-92-kilogram division\", \"from\": 1567, \"to\": 1602}, {\"ngram\": \"gold medal\", \"from\": 1604, \"to\": 1614}, {\"